snippet.title: The Showdown Effect - PC Gameplay 1080P
snippet.description:
Pretty funny Multiplayer Sidescroller. Gameplay from the Beta
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/clayman90
My Gaming Setup: http://youtu.be/77gaKbzeZNQ

The Showdown Effect is a 2.5D multiplayer action game
inspired by 80's and 90's action movies. 
Champions from throughout time fight to death for fun, 
for glory and for awesome.
http://www.paradoxplaza.com/games/the-showdown-effect
